g.inkscape:label: Report Accessibility
g.text: This tab shows accessibility issues, indicating problems for older users, people with disabilities and those with accessibility needs.
Priority A - accessibility users will find it impossible to use some pages
Priority AA - accessibility users will find it difficult to use some pages
Priority AAA - accessibility users will find it somewhat difficult to use some pages
Avoid animated images over 5 seconds long that can't be paused or stopped.
No TITLE attributes found for the frames on these pages.
Provide a way to skip repetitive navigation links.
This page has markup errors, causing screen readers to miss content.
Use semantic markup like STRONG instead of using the CSS font-weight property.
If you set any of the colors on the BODY tag you must set all of them.
Provide information about the site structure using a site map or table of contents.
